Inline-Lua version 0.05
=======================

Use inlined Lua code from Perl. See http://www.lua.org/ for details on Lua.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Inline
    Test::More
    Lua 5.0	library and header files (this module actually tested on 5.0.2)
    C compiler

